      "name": "Picus Exposure Validation",
      "description": "Picus Exposure Validation turns overwhelming vulnerability data into clear, evidence-based priorities. It safely simulates real-world attacks across cloud, network, and endpoint controls to reveal the exposures that are truly exploitable in an environment, helping organizations prioritize patching and reduce mean time to remediation.",
